  • public class LNSRequestInfo
extends Object
    Class represents the abstract class in which LNS stores info for each ongoing request, from the time it is received by a LNS until a success/failure response is returned. Only a single instance of this class is defined during the lifetime of a request. Some fields in this class are necessary to implement functionality of a local serviceName server, while some are there only to collect and log statistics for a request.
